;Usage
<pre>{{UCI code|team code}}</pre>
The parameter ''link=off'' can be added if it is desired to turn the link to [[Union Cycliste Internationale]] off, for instance of it has already been linked.
<pre>{{UCI code|team code|link=off}}</pre>
